  "info": {
    "name": "HT-CentralCashPool-CLM-Mirror-TimeEpoch-BiWeekly-7",
    "_postman_id": "ht-v11-central-cash-pool",
    "description": "HT v11 — Central Cash Pool. Extends v10 (split CLM Lending+Spot) by:\n  1. Removing inert CSH seed contract — $2.75M folded into CASH-PAM-3M notional\n  2. Adding ad_btc01_spot_mirror — SPOT CLM recalls now route to CASH-PAM (was free cash)\n  3. Adding scf_tbill_flows_01 (ScheduledCashFlowModel) — T-Bill IED outflows and MD inflows\n     now route through CASH-PAM as PP signals (Mar-01 -$750K, Mar-31 +$500K, May-31 +$500K,\n     Jun-30 +$250K, Jul-31 +$500K)\n  4. CASH-PAM-3M: notional=$5.75M, discount=-$4.75M → same net IED -$1M deployed\n     Initial NP=$5.75M represents consolidated cash pool ($3M PAM + $2.75M seed)\n  Allocation band: 20% target [15%–25%] UNCHANGED. Bi-weekly epochs Mar–Aug 2026.\n  Scenario: ht_v11_central_pool_scn01  |  Contracts: 7 (CSH removed)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
